      <title>Cent OS搭建SS与BBR</title>
      <link href="/2018/11/19/Cent%20OS%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BASS%E4%B8%8EBBR/"/>
      <url>/2018/11/19/Cent%20OS%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BASS%E4%B8%8EBBR/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="CentOS安装shadowsocks"><a href="#CentOS安装shadowsocks" class="headerlink" title="CentOS安装shadowsocks "></a>CentOS安装shadowsocks <span id="详细版"></span></h1><p>tip: 想直接动手，请<a href="#精简版">跳到最后</a></p><h3 id="1-用pip安装："><a href="#1-用pip安装：" class="headerlink" title="1. 用pip安装："></a>1. 用pip安装：</h3><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root<span class="symbol">@OffbeatEdible</span>-VM ~]<span class="meta">#pip install shadowsocks</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果提示：<br><code>-bash: pip: command not found</code>, 就是还没有安装pip,则 使用yum进行安装:<br><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root<span class="symbol">@OffbeatEdible</span>-VM ~]<span class="meta">#yum install python-pip</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>but, 出现了 Error :</strong><br><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@OffbeatEdible-VM ~]# yum install python-pip</span><br><span class="line">Loaded plugins: fastestmirror</span><br><span class="line">Loading<span class="built_in"> mirror </span>speeds <span class="keyword">from</span> cached hostfile</span><br><span class="line"> * base: mirror.fileplanet.com</span><br><span class="line"> * extras: mirrors.usc.edu</span><br><span class="line"> * updates: mirrors.usc.edu</span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">No</span> package python-pip available.</span><br><span class="line">Error: <span class="literal">Nothing</span> <span class="keyword">to</span> <span class="keyword">do</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>你就需要这样了：</strong><br><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root<span class="symbol">@OffbeatEdible</span>-VM ~]<span class="meta">#yum -y install epel-release</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>再重新执行</strong>： <code>yum install python-pip</code></p><ul><li>好了，可以执行 <code>pip install shadowsocks</code> , 好像成功了，但是：</li></ul><figure class="highlight livecodeserver"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Successfully installed shadowsocks<span class="number">-2.8</span><span class="number">.2</span></span><br><span class="line">You are <span class="keyword">using</span> pip <span class="built_in">version</span> <span class="number">8.1</span><span class="number">.2</span>, however <span class="built_in">version</span> <span class="number">18.1</span> is available.</span><br><span class="line">You should consider upgrading via <span class="keyword">the</span> <span class="string">'pip install --upgrade pip'</span> <span class="keyword">command</span>.</span><br><span class="line">Successfully installed shadowsocks<span class="number">-2.8</span><span class="number">.2</span></span><br><span class="line">You are <span class="keyword">using</span> pip <span class="built_in">version</span> <span class="number">8.1</span><span class="number">.2</span>, however <span class="built_in">version</span> <span class="number">18.1</span> is available.</span><br><span class="line">You should consider upgrading via <span class="keyword">the</span> <span class="string">'pip install --upgrade pip'</span> <span class="keyword">command</span>.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>有pip版本问题，如<code>You should consider upgrading via the &#39;pip install --upgrade pip&#39; command.</code> , 解决方法：<code>pip install --upgrade pip</code></strong></li></ul><h3 id="2-手动修改shadowsocks配置文件"><a href="#2-手动修改shadowsocks配置文件" class="headerlink" title="2. 手动修改shadowsocks配置文件"></a>2. 手动修改shadowsocks配置文件</h3><ul><li>用vi编辑器的命令（文件路径与名称可随意修改）： <code>vi /etc/shadowsocks.json</code></li><li><p>单端口：</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"local_address"</span>: <span class="string">"127.0.0.1"</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"local_port"</span>:<span class="number">1080</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"server_port"</span>:<span class="number">8888</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"password"</span>:<span class="string">"mypassword"</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"timeout"</span>:<span class="number">300</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"method"</span>:<span class="string">"aes-256-cfb"</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"fast_open"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>多个端口：</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"server"</span>:<span class="string">"0.0.0.0"</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"port_password"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"8888"</span>: <span class="string">"password"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"8889"</span>: <span class="string">"password"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"8890"</span>: <span class="string">"password"</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"timeout"</span>:<span class="number">300</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"method"</span>: <span class="string">"rc4-md5"</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">"fast_open"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="3-指定配置文件启动-shadowsocks-服务"><a href="#3-指定配置文件启动-shadowsocks-服务" class="headerlink" title="3. 指定配置文件启动 shadowsocks 服务"></a>3. 指定配置文件启动 shadowsocks 服务</h3><ul><li><strong>命令行</strong>：<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssserver -c /etc/shadowsocks<span class="selector-class">.json</span> -d start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>使用命令 <code>netstat -nlp</code>可查看端口上开启的服务</p><ul><li><strong>防火墙未开放端口导致无法连接</strong><br><strong>防火墙开放端口：</strong></li><li>CentOS 6默认使用的是iptables，开放端口命令为:<figure class="highlight pf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">iptables -I INPUT -m <span class="keyword">state</span> --state NEW -m tcp -p tcp --dport 需要加入的端口 -j ACCEPT</span><br><span class="line">iptables -I INPUT -m <span class="keyword">state</span> --state NEW -m udp -p udp --dport 需要加入的端口 -j ACCEPT</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>保存配置、重启防火墙的命令：<br><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta-keyword">/etc/</span>init.d/iptables save</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta-keyword">/etc/</span>init.d/iptables restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><ul><li>CentOS 7默认使用的是firewall，开放端口命令为:<figure class="highlight jboss-cli"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ifirewall-cmd <span class="params">--permanent</span> <span class="params">--zone=public</span> <span class="params">--add-port=</span>需要加入的端口<span class="string">/tcp</span></span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd <span class="params">--permanent</span> <span class="params">--zone=public</span> <span class="params">--add-port=</span>需要加入的端口<span class="string">/udp</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>重启防火墙的命令：<br><figure class="highlight dockerfile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-<span class="keyword">cmd</span><span class="bash"> --reload</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><ul><li><strong>使用客户端连接服务器，地址，端口，密码，加密方式要对应</strong><h3 id="4-服务加入开机自启动"><a href="#4-服务加入开机自启动" class="headerlink" title="4. 服务加入开机自启动"></a>4. 服务加入开机自启动</h3></li><li><p>编辑 /etc/rc.local,在其中将ss的启动命令添加进去，就能开机自启动了：</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo ssserver -c <span class="regexp">/etc/</span>shadowsocks.json</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>必须给 /etc/rc.local 赋予可执行权限：</p><figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod +x /etc/rc.<span class="keyword">local</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>可以重启测试是否可行：<br><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root<span class="symbol">@OffbeatEdible</span>-VM ~]<span class="meta"># reboot</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="至此，如无意外，shadowsocks已经可以使用。"><a href="#至此，如无意外，shadowsocks已经可以使用。" class="headerlink" title="至此，如无意外，shadowsocks已经可以使用。"></a><strong>至此，如无意外，shadowsocks已经可以使用。</strong></h2><h1 id="centos安装bbr加速"><a href="#centos安装bbr加速" class="headerlink" title="centos安装bbr加速"></a>centos安装bbr加速</h1><ul><li>安装bbr命令行:<figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root<span class="symbol">@OffbeatEdible</span>-VM ~]<span class="meta">#wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/teddysun/across/raw/master/bbr.sh</span></span><br><span class="line">[root<span class="symbol">@OffbeatEdible</span>-VM ~]<span class="meta"># chmod +x bbr.sh</span></span><br><span class="line">[root<span class="symbol">@OffbeatEdible</span>-VM ~]<span class="meta"># ./bbr.sh</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>接下来只需要等待安装，也许要几分钟，then:<br><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Complete!</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Info: The<span class="built_in"> system </span>needs <span class="keyword">to</span> reboot.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">Do</span> you want <span class="keyword">to</span> restart system? [y/n]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>不要重启！极有可能会开不了机</strong></p><ul><li><p>创建force-vitio_blk-to-ensure-boot.conf</p><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">'add_drivers+="virtio_blk"'</span> &gt;/etc/dracut.<span class="keyword">conf</span>.d/force-vitio_blk-<span class="keyword">to</span>-ensure-boot.<span class="keyword">conf</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>重新编译生成initramfs，把下面代码中的两个4.20.2-1.el7.elrepo.x86_64替换成你升级后新内核的版本号</p><figure class="highlight lsl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 我主机的命令</span><br><span class="line">[root@OffbeatEdible-VM ~]#dracut -f /boot/initramfs<span class="number">-4.20</span><span class="number">.2</span><span class="number">-1.</span>el7.elrepo.x86_64.img <span class="number">4.20</span><span class="number">.2</span><span class="number">-1.</span>el7.elrepo.x86_64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>你主机的命令应该为：<br><figure class="highlight jboss-cli"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dracut -f <span class="string">/boot/initramfs-</span>你的新内核的版本号<span class="string">.img</span> 新内核的版本号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><ul><li>不知道自己新内核版本号的话，用命令： <code>ls /lib/modules/</code> 查看</li></ul><p>然后再重启系统，<code>reboot</code></p><p>正常启动后，运行命令查看状态：<br><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-attr">[root@OffbeatEdible-VM ~]</span># <span class="selector-tag">sysctl</span> <span class="selector-tag">net</span><span class="selector-class">.ipv4</span><span class="selector-class">.tcp_congestion_control</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#显示结果：类似于：net<span class="selector-class">.ipv4</span><span class="selector-class">.tcp_congestion_control</span> = bbr</span><br><span class="line">net<span class="selector-class">.core</span><span class="selector-class">.default_qdisc</span></span><br><span class="line">net<span class="selector-class">.ipv4</span><span class="selector-class">.tcp_congestion_control</span> = bbr</span><br><span class="line">net<span class="selector-class">.core</span><span class="selector-class">.default_qdisc</span> = fq</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>ok,done.</strong></p><ul><li>若重启后无法登入系统，VNC连接查看屏幕提示“FATAL: Module scsi_wait_scan not found”。</li></ul><p><strong>解决方法（未实测）：</strong></p><ul><li>控制台中重启系统，重启过程中不断的尝试使用VNC连接，当连接成功且刚读秒时，按键盘的箭头↓键选择旧的内核。旧的内核可以正常启动，登入，重新开始创建force-vitio_blk-to-ensure-boot.conf </li></ul><hr><h1 id="精简版："><a href="#精简版：" class="headerlink" title="精简版："></a><span id="精简版">精简版：</span></h1><p>详细版请<a href="#详细版">回到顶部</a><br><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#安装shadowsocks &lt;-- 升级pip &lt;-- 安装python-pip</span></span><br><span class="line">yum -y <span class="keyword">install</span> epel-release</span><br><span class="line">yum <span class="keyword">install</span> python-pip</span><br><span class="line">pip <span class="keyword">install</span> --upgrade pip</span><br><span class="line">pip <span class="keyword">install</span> shadowsocks</span><br><span class="line">vi /etc/shadowsocks.json</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><figure class="highlight vala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta"># 多用户：</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"server"</span>:<span class="string">"0.0.0.0"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"port_password"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"8888"</span>: <span class="string">"password"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"8889"</span>: <span class="string">"password"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"8890"</span>: <span class="string">"password"</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"timeout"</span>:<span class="number">300</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"method"</span>: <span class="string">"rc4-md5"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"fast_open"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>保存退出： <code>：wq</code></strong><br><figure class="highlight jboss-cli"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 开启sserver服务</span></span><br><span class="line">ssserver -c <span class="string">/etc/shadowsocks.json</span> -d start</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># CentOS 7默认使用的是firewall，修改防火墙规则：</span></span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd <span class="params">--permanent</span> <span class="params">--zone=public</span> <span class="params">--add-port=</span>需要加入的端口<span class="string">/tcp</span></span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd <span class="params">--permanent</span> <span class="params">--zone=public</span> <span class="params">--add-port=</span>需要加入的端口<span class="string">/udp</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 重启防火墙</span></span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd <span class="params">--reload</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 配置开机启动服务，编辑/etc/rc.local文件：</span></span><br><span class="line">vi /etc/rc.local</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 加入ss的启动命令：</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo ssserver -c /etc/shadowsocks.json</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 赋予可执行权限：</span></span><br><span class="line">chmod +x /etc/rc.local</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 重启测试：</span></span><br><span class="line">reboot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><ul><li>安装BBR加速：<figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget --<span class="keyword">no</span>-check-certificate http<span class="variable">s:</span>//github.<span class="keyword">com</span>/teddysun/across/raw/master/bbr.<span class="keyword">sh</span></span><br><span class="line">chmod +<span class="keyword">x</span> bbr.<span class="keyword">sh</span></span><br><span class="line">./bbr.<span class="keyword">sh</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p><strong>不要重启</strong><br><figure class="highlight lsl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#修改内核：</span><br><span class="line">#创建force-vitio_blk-to-ensure-boot.conf</span><br><span class="line">echo 'add_drivers+=<span class="string">"virtio_blk"</span>' &gt;/etc/dracut.conf.d/force-vitio_blk-to-ensure-boot.conf</span><br><span class="line"># 重新编译生成initramfs，把下面代码中的两个<span class="number">4.20</span><span class="number">.2</span><span class="number">-1.</span>el7.elrepo.x86_64替换成你升级后新内核的版本号</span><br><span class="line">dracut -f /boot/initramfs<span class="number">-4.20</span><span class="number">.2</span><span class="number">-1.</span>el7.elrepo.x86_64.img <span class="number">4.20</span><span class="number">.2</span><span class="number">-1.</span>el7.elrepo.x86_64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><ul><li>不知道自己新内核版本号的话，用命令： <code>ls /lib/modules/</code> 查看<figure class="highlight jboss-cli"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dracut -f <span class="string">/boot/initramfs-</span>你的新内核的版本号<span class="string">.img</span> 新内核的版本号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
